iewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>July 12, 2026</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>9 min read</span></div><span class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700\">Read story <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></span></a><a class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/germany-old-names-revived\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-blue-700\">Country &amp; Regional Names</span><h2 class=\"nv-display mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 group-hover:text-blue-700\">Old German Names Being Revived by Young Parents</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">A distinct wave of German parents in their twenties and thirties are deliberately reaching back two generations for names their own great-grandparents wore.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-slate-500\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"2