t-slate-600\">Names that mean strength carry something more than a definition. They carry expectation, hope, and history. Here&#x27;s a thoughtful collection of the strongest names across cultures — with the stories behind them.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-slate-500\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>June 11, 2026</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>8 min read</span></div><span class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700\">Read story <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></span></a><a class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-avoid-baby-name-regret\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-blue-700\">Baby Naming Guides</span><h2 class=\"nv-display mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 group-hover:text-blue-700\">How to Avoid Baby Name Regret</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Baby name regret is more common than most people admit. Here&#x27;s how to slow down, think clearly, and choose a name you&#x27;ll still love years from now.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-slate-500\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>June 11, 2026</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>8 min read</span></div><span class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700\">Read story <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></span></a><a class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-choose-a-baby-name-that-stands-out\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-blue-700\">Baby Naming Guides</span><h2 class=\"nv-display mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 group-hover:text-blue-700\">How to Choose a Baby Name That Stands Out</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Choosing a baby name that stands out takes more than picking something unusual. This guide walks you through how to find a name that&#x27;s distinctive, meaningful, and built to last.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-slate-500\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>June 11, 2026</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>8 min read</span></div><span class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700\">Read story <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></span></a><a class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-choose-a-baby-name-with-meaning\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-blue-700\">Baby Naming Guides</span><h2 class=\"nv-display mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 group-hover:text-blue-700\">How to Choose a Baby Name With Meaning</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">A baby name with meaning is more than one with a nice dictionary entry. This guide shows you how to find names with genuine depth — names that connect to something real, personal, and lasting.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-slate-500\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>June 11, 2026</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>8 min read</span></div><span class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700\">Read story <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></span></a><a class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-choose-a-gender-neutral-baby-name\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-blue-700\">Baby Naming Guides</span><h2 class=\"nv-display mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 group-hover:text-blue-700\">How to Choose a Gender-Neutral Baby Name</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Gender-neutral baby names are more popular than ever — but choosing the right one takes more thought than simply picking whatever sounds unisex. Here&#x27;s a practical guide to doing it well.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-slate-500\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>June 11, 2026</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>8 min read</span></div><span class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700\">Read story <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></span></a><a class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-pick-a-unique-baby-boy-name\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-blue-700\">Baby Naming Guides</span><h2 class=\"nv-display mt-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950 group-hover:text-blue-700\">How to Pick a Unique Baby Boy Name</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Looking for a unique baby boy name that isn&#x27;t just rare for the sake of it? This guide shows you where to look, what to avoid, and how to find a name that genuinely stands out.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-slate-500\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg>June 11, 2026</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>8 min read</span></div><span class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700\">Read story <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></span></a></section></main></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div></div><footer class=\"border-t border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.3f